Cell["\<\
Styles can combine with PlotTheme and have a higher precedence. Here, \
FrameStyle is used instead of AxesStyle because PlotTheme often converts axes \
to frames:\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"451d3c16-a5cd-48cb-ae57-ee67b744cfba"],

